commitResults.messageBody:
When using unmark and delete, call to Storage.deleteFromFile function
fires, saving the information to data/tasks.txt

Storage.deleteFromFile does not delete the information from
data/tasks.txt properly, causing the program to crash in the next
instance of running

Let's,
* update the Storage.deleteFromFile method to properly delete information
from the data/tasks.txt
* fix the unmark/mark and delete commands to use the proper Storage and
Parser class methods
